# Keep the Docker build context tiny and secret-free.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/.venv
**/venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov
**/build
**/dist
**/*.egg-info
**/node_modules
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/README.md
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.log
**/data/references
**/data/demo
**/data/cache
**/workspaces
